  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, W-ON-01 trigger)",
  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) operating conditions. The intended use scope — absolute hemolysis index prediction for a Class III VAD at Model Risk Level 5 — is described in the Claim and Requirement prose. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed; all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated. Decision: Accepted under ProfileMinimal. NOTE: structured hasContextOfUse link is intentionally absent (W-ON-01); use scope is implied only by Claim/Requirement narrative.",
