    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under ProfileMinimal, the assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for the VAD intended-use scope described in the Claim and Requirement narratives. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels, and six factors carry epistemic-gap flags. The team acknowledged these shortfalls but determined that the overall evidence package meets the threshold for a Low assurance level submission under the minimal profile. The structured Context of Use object was not formally linked; use scope is recoverable from prose in bindsRequirement and bindsClaim nodes.",
